apLibre\/MLNOfflinePack","type":"reference"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"object’s progress changes. The progress may change due to a resource being","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"downloaded or because the pack discovers during the download that more","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"resources are required for offline viewing. This notification is posted","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"whenever any field in the ","type":"text"},{"code":"progress","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" property changes.","type":"text"}],"title":"MLNOfflinePackProgressChangedNotification","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackProgressChangedNotification","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNOfflinePackProgressChangedNotification"}]}}}